{
	"name": "Indomitable Squad",
	"type": "feat",
	"img": "icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p>You can now use your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.XXB8JdlvKIksSmR7]{Indomitable} ability to affect your allies.</p><p><strong>Reaction</strong> - All Allies (60 ft.)</p><p><em>Trigger: You or an ally within 60 ft. of you fails a saving throw.</em></p><ul><li><p>Choose as many allies as you want (including yourself) who failed the saving throw. Roll [[/r 1d10]] and add the number to the saving throws of all chosen allies. If at least one chosen ally passes their saving throw, you expend one use of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.XXB8JdlvKIksSmR7]{Indomitable}.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><em>This could apply to a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.057CZWwhMSyXT0M3]{Disintegrate} spell affecting a single ally, or a dragon's breath weapon targeting several of your allies.</em></p>",
